cs.DS, cs.LG, cs.DM, cs.IT, cs.SI. 

The paper deals with clustering in data streams, which is a problem in data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG). The problem of correlation clustering is a classic problem in theoretical computer science (cs.DM) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of linear sketches and convex programming also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to the sub-category of signal processing (cs.SI).
